        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer97993977" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12404224047350192547">This is an unforgetable book, with vivid tales of the children lost in the great blizzard of 1888 in the Dakota territory,Minnesota, Nebraska, Iowa and Kansas. I have only been in one blizzard in my life and the news said &quot;Do Not Go Outside, You will die&quot;. There were many tragic deaths blames on this blizzard. Many children never made it home from school, some lost parts of their body but many lost their lives. Very sad, I wish that everyone would read this book.</span>
  <span id="freeText12404224047350192547" style="display:none">This is an unforgetable book, with vivid tales of the children lost in the great blizzard of 1888 in the Dakota territory,Minnesota, Nebraska, Iowa and Kansas. I have only been in one blizzard in my life and the news said "Do Not Go Outside, You will die". There were many tragic deaths blames on this blizzard. Many children never made it home from school, some lost parts of their body but many lost their lives. Very sad, I wish that everyone would read this book.</span>
