              <span id="reviewTextContainer2679060628" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2550368006969892386">This book was an astonishing history and chronicle of this monstrous blizzard in 1888. The author goes in depth to the emigrant Homesteading stories and background of the Signal Corps now known as the National Weather Service. It is fascinating reading but left me heavy hearted at the toll of lives lost, so many of them children. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


